{
  "stem": "24195.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, that's-- that's the word that they have used-- were used for Jews and gypsies and others.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I mean, this you know, was unthinkable by German terms to think that they would be honorable of a-- you know, they would never use-- the German army never used them.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you couldn't think that the US Army did, because they're not familiar with life in the-- in the United States.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, so that was-- so in any case, that was an event, again, that made us feel good.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we saw, gee, we're drawing toward the close or the end.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's obvious-- I mean, Germany is not going to win this war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, they're-- they're destroying everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This airfield-- those jets-- jets never returned.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They couldn't return, because they had systematically, completely laid rows of you know, bombs across-- they you know, dropped them across the airfields in all the-- in so-- in so many areas that it was impossible to land for any plane or take off.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The runways were totally destroyed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So actually, our-- our work was-- was finished.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, there was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Although they had said we were going to you know, immediately go and trying to rebuild everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was like the-- it was the end of March, I think.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was like, March 31st or something like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1945, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And March 31st.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then after that, yeah, they made us-- yeah, they ordered us to clean up the next day and try and-- but there was really hardly anything to do.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The destruction was so-- massive that there was no way that the-- it was inhumanly to even think of you know, to-- rebuild this airfield.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
